## Repository Structure

```
pantheon_translation_engine/
├── ingest/          # Source parsers (text, JSON, YAML, code)
├── reduce/          # Extraction: entities, relations, constraints
├── ir/              # Intermediate representation (ThoughtObject)
├── targets/         # Output renderers (prose, JSON, YAML, Python, graph)
├── audit/           # Fidelity, reversibility, constraint checks
└── main.py
```

