## Relation to PantheonOS

The Translation Engine is not a standalone tool.  
It is one of the clearest practical manifestations of the Pantheon architecture.

Internal daemon mappings:

- **Spider** — structural extraction from messy inputs
- **Mirror** — integrity and constraint verification
- **Dragonfly** — coordinate transforms between representations
- **Raven** — compression without core loss
- **Blacksmith** — invariant satisfaction testing

